metadata.name: FXCK LAB
metadata.description:
FxckFace was launched last year as a Profile Picture NFT by Elite Syrup. It's a collection of 5,000 handmade, hand-drawn, hand-generated, hand-minted, without code, and was sold out in a month. 
.
We made this picture to announce that we are working on our first Generative collection, "Fxckface Hero"
.
For those who bought this piece what you will get is 
1. Rare of FxckFace Genesis 1 pc.
2. Whitelist for the upcoming Fxckface Hero to be launched
